lead_paragraph: Robert Scheidt, one of three Olympic sailors to win five medals, two of them gold, reckons he has a good chance of making it six when racing begins on Aug. 8 at home in Rio de Janeiro.

headline.print_headline: Laser's 'El Demolidor' Seeks Last Medal at Home
